text.section:
An eligible company shall certify to the authority, by written application provided by the authority, the following:
That the company is making a minimum investment of one hundred thousand dollars ($100,000) in the project, if the project is located in a preference zone or five hundred thousand dollars ($500,000) in the project, if the project is not located in a preference zone;
A description of the project;
An estimate of the expenses for which the company shall seek approval;
Supporting documentation, as requested by the authority; and
Any other information requested by the authority.
